    "Table 2 1, Table 3, Table 4, and Table 5 show the performance comparison between recent approaches and CONSOLE, where we can find that CON-SOLE outperforms the strong baselines HAMT [16] and DUET [24] consistently on R2R, REVERIE, R4R, and RxR especially in unseen scenarios (e.g., CONSOLE outperforms DUET in SPL by 3% and 2% under Val Unseen and Test Unseen on R2R, respectively).",
